abstracts.cdata!:
The Fourth Highway Project will finance
            construction of the Yabayo-Gagnoa road (79 km) and of a two
            lane bridge over the N'Zi river; supervision of
            construction by consultants, and a feeder road study for the
            cotton growing areas of the Ivory Coast.
